- Don't: Relying only on all-match fixtures for agents with scoped execution behavior
- Do: Add scenario fixtures for CHANGED_FILES pointing to non-workflow paths (expect SKIP); Add scenario fixtures for CHANGED_FILES with one workflow file (expect targeted actionlint invocation path behavior)

